  "detailed_description": "Explore a surreal and mystical island as you search for the ancient Manaliths. Discover beautiful vistas, secret passages, and dozens of items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1408810/extras/5cad9356f3df988a7a7985b1c773b500.poster.avif?t=1628639043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1408810/extras/5cad9356f3df988a7a7985b1c773b500.webm?t=1628639043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1408810/extras/5cad9356f3df988a7a7985b1c773b500.mp4?t=1628639043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Walk, run, climb, swim, and glide through meadows, woods, jungles, and caverns.<br></li><li>Forge your own path, exploring the island however you wish.<br></li><li>Use your magic to summon mystical torches to light your way, sense nearby items, blast through secret walls, and fast-travel across the island.<br></li><li>Collect items that extend your stamina, improve your magical abilities, and more.<br></li><li>Wander and explore at your own pace, without dodging traps, fighting enemies, or scrounging for questionable foods.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1408810/extras/14f310e1af7759149b62ce586b2ee2f1.poster.avif?t=1628639043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1408810/extras/14f310e1af7759149b62ce586b2ee2f1.webm?t=1628639043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1408810/extras/14f310e1af7759149b62ce586b2ee2f1.mp4?t=1628639043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
